General introduction:
--------------------
openBibleViewer is a Bible study application based on Qt 4.5 or later.

If you found a bug, please report him on http://openbv.uucyc.name/bug/.

Read the file INSTALL how to install and compile this version of openBibleViewer. There's also a SPEC file
to create RPMs, it's called openBibleViewer.spec.

Requirements:
-------------
See file INSTALL for detailed installation instructions.

Documentation:
--------------
You can find information about openBibleViewer, the installation and its usage on the website: http://openbv.uucyc.name/en


Paul Walger
